OL,3,CPolice hunt for man, 25, after six
OL,4,Ccharged over Knightsbridge fatal
OL,5,Cstabbing
OL,7,FPolice are hunting for a 25-year-old
OL,8,Fman after six others were charged over
OL,9,Fthe fatal stabbing of a 24-year-old
OL,10,Fnear a luxury hotel in central London.
OL,12,FBlue Stevens, a young father, died
OL,13,Fafter he was attacked in Seville
OL,14,FStreet, Knightsbridge in July 2025.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the Metropolitan Police
OL,17,Fsaid six men had been charged with
OL,18,Fperverting the course of justice.
