OL,7,F"We are pleading with anyone who has
OL,8,Fany information about this crime or
OL,9,Fthe offender to come forward. Any
OL,10,Finformation, no matter how small,
OL,11,Fcould help our children to know their
OL,12,Ffather's life mattered."
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Samantha
OL,15,FTownsend, from the Met's Specialist
OL,16,FCrime Command, said: "We continue to
OL,17,Ffollow every possible line of enquiry
OL,18,Fas part of our investigation.
